short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Updates web-browsing experience by creating a more accurate representation of Donald Trump

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Donald Trump has whined his way into the presidency of the United States. Referencing the term coined by Bill Maher, this replaces 'Donald Trump' with 'Donald Whiny Lil Bitch' and justifiably replaces images of him with a caricature of his toddler-like personality.
